data.description: Come check out this fabulous updated home for a growing family. The extra large family room boasts a beautiful coffered ceiling. Four roomy bedroom; each with direct access to a bathroom and great closest space. New luxury LVT flooring, high ceilings, recent paint and roof. Remodeled kitchen with new dishwasher and stove. Covered rear patio with extra large lot. Three car garage parking with storage. Wonderful neighborhood! So many great features! Call for your showing today.
